--*
--* CLASSES: ORDERED_PARTIAL_SET(K<ORDERED(K),T1,T<ORDERED_PARTIAL(K,T),ORDER<ORDER_RELATION(T)) EXCEPTION__ORDERED_PARTIAL_SET_NEXT EXCEPTION__ORDERED_PARTIAL_SET_PREVIOUS
--* 
--* IMPLEMENTATION OF: 
--*
--* CONFORMS TO: ORDERED_SET(T,ORDER) PARTIAL_SET(K,T1,T)
--*
--* IS A: ORDERED_PARTIAL_MULTISET(K,T1,T,ORDER) 
--*
--* REQUIRED CLASSES: ORDERED_SET(T,ORDER) ORDER_RELATION(T) ORDERED_PARTIAL(K,T) \
--* ORDER_LT(T) PARTIAL_SET(K,T1,T) ORDERED_PARTIAL_INT ORDERED_PARTIAL_MULTISET \
--* EXCEPTION__MULTISET EXCEPTION__PARTIAL_MULTISET_LOOKUP EXCEPTION__SET_ADD \
--* EXCEPTION__SET_DISJOINT_UNION EXCEPTION__ORDERED_MULTISET_MIN \
--* EXCEPTION__ORDERED_MULTISET_MAX EXCEPTION__ORDERED_MULTISET_NEXT \
--* EXCEPTION__ORDERED_MULTISET_PREVIOUS EXCEPTION__ORDERED_PARTIAL_MULTISET_NEXT \
--* EXCEPTION__ORDERED_PARTIAL_MULTISET_PREVIOUS
--*
--* EXCEPTIONS: EXCEPTION__MULTISET EXCEPTION__PARTIAL_MULTISET_LOOKUP \
--* EXCEPTION__SET_ADD EXCEPTION__SET_DISJOINT_UNION EXCEPTION__ORDERED_MULTISET_MIN \
--* EXCEPTION__ORDERED_MULTISET_MAX EXCEPTION__ORDERED_MULTISET_NEXT \
--* EXCEPTION__ORDERED_MULTISET_PREVIOUS EXCEPTION__ORDERED_PARTIAL_MULTISET_NEXT \
--* EXCEPTION__ORDERED_PARTIAL_MULTISET_PREVIOUS
--*
--* TEST CLASS: TEST__ORDERED_PARTIAL_SET
--*
--* FOREIGN FILES:
--*
